
--- Network Analysis ---

• Tools
• Packet Capture
• Analyze with Wireshark
• IDS / Snort



🔧 Tools: Wireshark / tcpdump / Zeek / Snort


📡 Packet Capture

sudo tcpdump -i eth0 -w capture.pcap
sudo tcpdump -i eth0 host 192.168.1.10 and port 443


🔍 Analyze with Wireshark

http.request.method == "POST"
tls.handshake.extensions_server_name
dns.qry.name contains "suspiciousdomain.com"


🚨 IDS / Snort

snort -A console -c /etc/snort/snort.conf -i eth0
alert tcp any any -> any 80 (content:"/cmd.exe"; msg:"Possible CMD Execution"; sid:1000001;)
